 a user profile manager configured to store associations between users of the motor vehicle and respective personal electronic devices; and   a wireless connection manager communicatively coupled to the user profile manager, the wireless connection manager being configured to:
 detect that a personal electronic device is in a vicinity of the vehicle; 
 refer to the user profile manager to determine whether the personal electronic device is a primary personal electronic device of a current user of the vehicle; 
 if it is determined that the personal electronic device is a primary personal electronic device of a current user of the vehicle, establish a wireless connection between the personal electronic devices and the vehicle; and
